elements.description: Please indicate whether you experienced any of the following sensations, feelings, or actions, and if so, to what extent:

questions.text: Tears
Chills or shivers
A warm feeling in the center of the chest.
Choked up.
Refreshed, energized, or exhilarated.

elements.description: Please rate to what extent each of the following statements are true:

questions.text: I felt/observed an extraordinary feeling of welcoming or being welcomed.
I felt/observed an exceptional sense of closeness appear.
I had positive feelings.
I was moved.
I was touched.
To what extent do you think audience members in your vicinity were moved?
To what extent did you feel connected to the musicians?
To what extent did you feel connected to others in the audience?
To what extent were you engrossed in your own world?
To what extent did you daydream?
To what extent were you distracted by thoughts or concerns of a personal nature?
To what extent were you attentive towards the music without distracting thoughts, memories, or actions?
